Angel voice, atarashii, natsukashii echo

11
00:01:17,677 --> 00:01:28,349
Shining smile, isogazu ni arinomama, kiss

12
00:01:34,527 --> 00:01:38,331
Mokkori Beauty, Ms. Misa, who came
